{"tid":1436123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運動突破點：每人行多一步","createTime":"2019-08-09T08:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T10:05:31.000Z","uid":131122,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1390524d9857f7a255cd8e9600775884a954a95d","tid":1436123,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"持續兩個月既運動，五大訴求一個都未有回應<br />\n和理非大罷工做左<br />\n勇武抗爭做左<br />\n但對手既龐大輿論機器呢排已經出盡力<br />\n又whatsapp瘋傳<br />\n又尻up影響經濟<br />\n又愛國團體<br />\n又大力抹黑示威者<br />\n而我地既反攻就得記者會<br />\n對家既資源既龐大實在大到好似一部推土機咁，慢慢一步一步輾壓落黎，根本難以迴避<br />\n如果再無突破點，運動會失敗只係時間問題<br />\n集中營再聚都已經不是夢<br />\n所以我跪求咁多位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日起每人行多一步啦</span></span><br />\n唔想入集中營既你，如果<br />\n平時只係純粹參加遊行：今日開始落區派傳單／整連儂牆<br />\n平時已經有派開傳單：落區搞放映會<br />\n平時已經有做過放映會：嘗試係多人既地方解釋清楚整件事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">向集中營說不</span>"},{"pid":"2ec864a8cf311582659ccb0371aac925f8f6fcdf","tid":1436123,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"400f87284201c90822f41b06afb4f794a84c7cad","tid":1436123,"uid":230882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:56:28.000Z","msg":"無錯，除咗上面講嘅仲可以參與罷買，每個人行多一步做多一啲<br />\n<br />\n「驚就唔好出街！」BYE BUY DAY 全城罷買投票結果出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436025</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqVTPvJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqVTPvJ.jpg&h=58ce9eff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLcnHQJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLcnHQJ.jpg&h=6d53abf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a2d700ef5437aaff187b9865a948b2572ed1fd5","tid":1436123,"uid":289124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad40b9b68e194